      "options": {
        "content": "<div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:8px 16px;background:rgba(12,18,30,0.8);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(0,242,254,0.2);font-family:Rajdhani,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:Orbitron,sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:2px\">APEX <span style=\"color:#00F2FE\">COMMAND</span></span><span style=\"font-size:13px;letter-spacing:1px\"><a href=\"/d/ims-noc-overview\" style=\"color:#E2E8F0;text-decoration:none\">NOC OVERVIEW</a> &nbsp;|&nbsp; <a href=\"/d/ims-engineering\" style=\"color:#E2E8F0;text-decoration:none\">ENG DRILL-DOWN</a> &nbsp;|&nbsp; <a href=\"/d/ims-capacity\" style=\"color:#E2E8F0;text-decoration:none\">CAPACITY FORECAST</a> &nbsp;|&nbsp; <a href=\"/d/ims-v2-diagnostics\" style=\"color:#00FF87;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none\">DIAGNOSTICS</a></span></div>\n<style>\n@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Rajdhani:wght@500;700&family=Orbitron:wght@400;700&display=swap');\n.dashboard-page { background: radial-gradient(circle at center, #0B0E14 0%, #030407 100%) !important; }\n.panel-container {\n  background: rgba(12, 18, 30, 0.6) !important;\n  border: 1px solid rgba(0, 242, 254, 0.15) !important;\n  border-radius: 8px !important;\n  box-shadow: 0 4px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5) !important;\n  transition: all 0.3s ease;\n  animation: fadeUp 0.5s ease-out forwards;\n}\n.panel-container:hover {\n  border-color: rgba(0, 255, 135, 0.4) !important;\n  box-shadow: 0 4px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5), inset 0 0 20px rgba(0, 255, 135, 0.05) !important;\n  backdrop-filter: blur(10px) !important;\n  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px) !important;\n  will-change: backdrop-filter;\n}\n.panel-title { font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 1px !important; color: #E2E8F0 !important; }\n.status-dot {\n  width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; background: #00FF87;\n  display: inline-block; margin-right: 8px;\n  animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;\n  box-shadow: 0 0 8px #00FF87;\n}\n@keyframes pulse { 0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); } 50% { opacity: 0.4; transform: scale(0.8); } }\n@keyframes fadeUp { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(15px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }\n</style>\n# ✅ System V2 Diagnostics\nThis dashboard verifies the 3 core improvements of the Phase 1-3 architecture:\n1. **Null-Handling**: When a machine goes offline, metrics are skipped rather than logged as zero. You will see gaps instead of line drops.\n2. **Dynamic Network Interfaces**: Every active interface is captured dynamically. See the panels below.\n3. **Decentralized Parsing**: The new Node-RED parser architecture accurately captures CPU, Storage, and LDI stats concurrently.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
